\lim_{x\to\infty}\frac{x^2}{1+x^2}=1?
\frac{x^2}{1+x^2}=\frac{x^2\cdot\frac1{x^2}}{(1+x^2)\cdot\frac1{x^2}}=\frac{1}{\frac1{x^2}+1}
