\lim\limits_{x\to\infty}\frac {1}{1+\frac 1 {x^2}}=1
\frac {x^2}{x^2+1}=\frac {x^2+1}{x^2+1}-\frac{1} {x^2+1}=1-\frac 1 {x^2+1}
\lim\limits_{x\to\infty}\frac 1 {x^2+1}=0
